Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.81,0:01:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,骗人  真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.74,0:01:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且还是在比赛中啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.59,0:01:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,选手们都在拼命比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.39,0:01:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,教练却在那里呼呼大睡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.05,0:01:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是难以置信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.51,0:01:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.81,0:01:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,午安 水月前辈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.54,0:01:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小茜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.69,0:01:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小茜你呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.83,0:01:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要吓人好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.85,0:01:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 前辈 听我说听我说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.77,0:02:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我改了摆臂的方式了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.09,0:02:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,摆臂？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.68,0:02:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我仔细研究了上周的比赛录像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.90,0:02:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,录像？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.85,0:02:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉手臂就像是滑过水面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.57,0:02:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是那样的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.96,0:02:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,动作是那样的美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.87,0:02:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一举一动都印在了我的脑海里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.11,0:02:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小茜 你是从哪里看到那个录像的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.10,0:02:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个是我拜托姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.25,0:02:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说过不要说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.84,0:02:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.09,0:02:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是遥吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.45,0:02:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很丢人的 不是叫你别再这么做了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.01,0:02:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为小茜说实在很想看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.89,0:02:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高梨教练也拜托…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.16,0:02:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.35,0:02:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  我不理遥了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.07,0:02:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都已经道歉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.94,0:02:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前辈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.78,0:02:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.10,0:02:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个...那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.37,0:02:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.72,0:02:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你们会吵架...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.68,0:03:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.57,0:03:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小茜真的慌了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.29,0:03:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们怎么可能吵架嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.76,0:03:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.81,0:03:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.08,0:03:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回家路上小心哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.33,0:03:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,速濑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.83,0:03:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发什么呆呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.26,0:03:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.08,0:03:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.94,0:04:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天气真好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.93,0:04:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小茜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.11,0:04:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事 姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.66,0:04:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天孝之会来吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.05,0:04:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好想见他呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.08,0:04:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行呀 姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.66,0:04:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥他忙着复习备考呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.63,0:04:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.59,0:04:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是考生啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.64,0:04:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.88,0:04:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天还没给花换水呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.85,0:04:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我先去一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.73,0:04:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,探望者须经过主治医生\N香月素子（内线52）许可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.94,0:05:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…还去看她吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.09,0:05:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.57,0:05:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我有责任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.02,0:05:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等遥好起来…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.56,0:05:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.90,0:05:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就跟她说我们的事情吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.32,0:05:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 会说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.56,0:05:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孝之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.96,0:05:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.62,0:05:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天上班时路过了白陵附中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.38,0:05:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍微瞄了一眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.87,0:05:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发现已经变了很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.79,0:05:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好象就是一所陌生的学校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.81,0:05:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们经历了很多事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.02,0:05:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很多事也都改变了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.05,0:05:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我却还没有完全接受这样的事实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.38,0:06:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.43,0:06:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只有孝之了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.90,0:06:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除了孝之 我什么都…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.91,0:06:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.49,0:06:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孝之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.87,0:06:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.18,0:06:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你  孝之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.42,0:06:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,简直就是给动物吃食嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.64,0:06:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就当没看见吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.25,0:06:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我什么时候变成养狗的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.67,0:06:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是干不下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.83,0:07:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 放开我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.40,0:07:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.58,0:07:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想去哪儿就去哪儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.99,0:07:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪里我不管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.55,0:07:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先把3号桌收拾干净
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.87,0:07:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去做啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.53,0:07:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  来一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.04,0:07:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么 放开我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.88,0:07:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫"你去做"啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.71,0:07:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你今天一次都没有收拾过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.40,0:07:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放开我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.68,0:07:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3号桌拜托你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.31,0:07:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁会去  笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.26,0:07:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又来了 真是玩不厌啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.27,0:07:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算是每天的必修课吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.21,0:07:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.95,0:07:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸣海君
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.63,0:07:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.58,0:07:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在方便吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.60,0:07:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是  有什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.36,0:07:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,实际上我想和鸣海谈谈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.75,0:07:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经拜托玉野收拾桌子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.89,0:07:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大空寺 就请你去帮她吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.89,0:07:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3号桌拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.67,0:07:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3号桌拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.11,0:08:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去踩猫屎吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.03,0:08:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁去踩啊  傻瓜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.65,0:08:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店长  要谈什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.67,0:08:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实是今晚突然缺人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.08,0:08:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以的话想请你帮忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.56,0:08:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚上吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.98,0:08:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.93,0:08:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 今晚...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.38,0:08:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又要去幽会吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.06,0:08:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幽会 幽会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.21,0:08:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么  真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.38,0:08:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这个只知道幽会的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.25,0:08:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好做点工作吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.76,0:08:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是你才对  真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.40,0:08:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸣海君
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.20,0:08:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就留在这里就职吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.03,0:08:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能对付那个吵人的家伙的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.01,0:08:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就只有你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.25,0:09:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦 鸣海君
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.73,0:09:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.75,0:09:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.29,0:09:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见 我明天再来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.12,0:09:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知悔改呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.83,0:09:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.55,0:09:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.58,0:09:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遥怎样了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.28,0:09:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很平静
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.21,0:09:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,记忆力的问题吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.87,0:09:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来还得花点时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.16,0:09:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 她似乎记得你来过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.21,0:09:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是...吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.90,0:09:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.07,0:09:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 孝之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.68,0:09:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我又来看你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.85,0:10:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.90,0:10:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知怎么的 日子过得特别快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.13,0:10:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才想着是早上 马上就傍晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.18,0:10:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后是晚上  转眼又早上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.40,0:10:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,觉得…觉得有些可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.69,0:10:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好暖和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.81,0:10:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很安心的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.78,0:10:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遥 那个...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.39,0:10:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来念咒语吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.89,0:10:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咒语
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.10,0:10:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如同无限夜空中的闪烁群星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.96,0:10:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的心交织在一起不分离
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.67,0:10:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使两人无法牵手…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.13,0:10:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遥 那个等你好了以后再说吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.09,0:11:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知怎么的 日子过得特别快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.07,0:11:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 鸣海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.15,0:11:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我原以为你不会再来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.15,0:11:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很感谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.32,0:11:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以的话 还能继续来看遥吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.98,0:11:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遥她一个劲的在说鸣海君的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.98,0:11:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直说  一直说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.35,0:11:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,记忆混乱早晚会好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.19,0:11:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是为了那一天的到来...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.38,0:11:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道我们没有立场拜托你这样的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.95,0:11:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一边叫你别再来一边却...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.73,0:12:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 现在的遥很需要你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.29,0:12:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了遥 请一定过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.17,0:12:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"尽量"也不要紧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.61,0:12:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.32,0:12:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我每天都来 决不间断
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.19,0:12:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为 对我来说 遥曾经是最重要的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.78,0:12:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,曾经…吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.19,0:12:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回来啦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.09,0:12:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.17,0:12:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃饱了 很好吃哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.05,0:12:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.13,0:12:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去泡茶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.86,0:12:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遥怎样了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.06,0:13:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.68,0:13:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道孝之是第二次去吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.45,0:13:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 记得很清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.87,0:13:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.83,0:13:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.30,0:13:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然记得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.92,0:13:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还问我今天你为什么不来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.21,0:13:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.62,0:13:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.79,0:13:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.49,0:13:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不回去没关系吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.39,0:13:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天还要早起的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.12,0:13:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我送你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.93,0:13:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我住在这里…可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.36,0:13:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不介意啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.61,0:13:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.07,0:14:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚的课题怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.50,0:14:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全听不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.49,0:14:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真讨厌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.87,0:14:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孝之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.81,0:14:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢 {\fn汉鼎简中圆}慎 {\fn汉鼎繁中圆}二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.94,0:14:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  要你过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.14,0:14:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天一堆课
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.81,0:14:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 是我打电话找你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.30,0:14:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天不打工？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.87,0:14:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,休息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.97,0:14:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.37,0:14:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美纪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.86,0:14:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去听"预言的哲学"吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.66,0:14:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 大概
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.20,0:14:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那一会儿见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.95,0:14:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很可爱啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.33,0:14:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道她就是上次说的那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.07,0:14:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.88,0:14:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放你鸽子的那个？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.99,0:14:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有希望吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.23,0:14:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.36,0:14:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我只是这么想而已…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.21,0:14:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油  你喜欢她吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.15,0:15:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样呀 凉宫现在这个样子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.40,0:15:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么说 你要一直去探望她？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.63,0:15:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我有责任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.93,0:15:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的只是责任？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.10,0:15:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你仍对凉宫…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.24,0:15:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.74,0:15:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你肯定吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.38,0:15:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就好 不要背叛速濑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.25,0:15:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙其实脆弱得很
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.22,0:15:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.45,0:15:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.04,0:15:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但在速濑面前要展现笑脸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.00,0:15:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.47,0:15:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢她的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.60,0:15:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.52,0:15:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,羽泽商贸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.12,0:15:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是  是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.67,0:15:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直承蒙您关照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.08,0:16:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,商品在周末一定送到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.07,0:16:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是  多多关照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.28,0:16:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你站那里干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.79,0:16:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小茜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.30,0:16:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐现在睡着了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.86,0:16:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.49,0:16:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你是这么迟钝的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.16,0:16:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都说到那个地步了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.07,0:16:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也想和你谈谈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.15,0:16:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谈什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.48,0:16:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和鸣海的事吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.46,0:16:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别弄脏我的耳朵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.71,0:16:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不理解也没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.08,0:16:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是想好好地和你谈谈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.86,0:16:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是让人吃惊的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.19,0:17:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只想着让自己解脱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.47,0:17:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全都说出来让自己轻松
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.34,0:17:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只想着自己可以忘记痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.91,0:17:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这个人还真不好相处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.49,0:17:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是 我没有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.58,0:17:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请回吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.04,0:17:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你必须更加痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.34,0:17:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能让你解脱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.50,0:17:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.98,0:17:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小茜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.38,0:17:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在这种地方做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.33,0:17:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.09,0:17:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你每天都很热心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.56,0:17:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明没这份心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.02,0:18:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸣海…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.84,0:18:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 孝之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.47,0:18:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,午安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.26,0:18:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 男朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.52,0:18:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.14,0:18:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在外面等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.50,0:18:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 已经完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.01,0:18:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来得正好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.55,0:18:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她今天状况很好  对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.28,0:18:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.15,0:18:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.26,0:18:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.10,0:18:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么接下去拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.70,0:18:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孝之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.38,0:18:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.49,0:19:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只想着自己可以忘记痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.13,0:19:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才没有做过那种事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.07,0:19:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别骗我了  我听速濑说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.72,0:19:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你体能测试的时候穿着可爱的长筒靴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.80,0:19:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水月太过分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.61,0:19:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明约定过不告诉别人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.07,0:19:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是50米跑吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.14,0:19:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然穿长筒靴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.29,0:19:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为早上下雨了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.81,0:19:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不带换的鞋啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.96,0:19:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之后才注意到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.78,0:19:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别再说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.44,0:19:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很丢人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.99,0:19:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这事传得很开呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.87,0:19:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没想到就是遥啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.48,0:19:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孝之 嘲笑得太过份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.94,0:19:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.95,0:19:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.05,0:19:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是很高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.55,0:19:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜欢孝之的笑容了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.42,0:19:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.85,0:20:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,复习怎么样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.61,0:20:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,顺利吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.14,0:20:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.99,0:20:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 我也好想回去学习啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.93,0:20:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我开始觉得不安了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.21,0:20:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的  总之不要心慌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.95,0:20:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切都等你身体好了以后再说吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.63,0:20:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.35,0:20:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有孝之在我身边太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.47,0:20:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还记得那个咒语吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.71,0:20:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,念吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.22,0:20:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忘了？
